    "Although proprietary systems might emphasise confidentiality to preserve a competitive advantage, it is crucial to balance commercial interests with the broader imperative for accountability and trust in AI technologies.",
    "We recommend the following practices to enhance transparency. 1.",
    "Availability of Training Data: Since the training dataset influences the model's behaviour and can perpetuate biases, ensuring its availability is essential. 2.",
    "Availability of Knowledge Bases: Many systems utilise various knowledge bases, such as taxonomies and vocabularies of research areas, to enhance performance.",
    "These resources should be made accessible for user inspection. 3."
  ],
